        <glossentry xml:id="gloss-package-identifier">
            <glossterm>Package Identifier</glossterm>
            <glossdef>
                <para>The Package Identifier allows any instance of an <xref linkend="gloss-epub-publication"/>
                    to be compared against another to determine if they are identical, different
                    versions of the same publication or unrelated.</para>
                <para>Refer to <olink targetdoc="publications" targetptr="sec-opf-metadata-identifiers-pid" 
